These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: tea, iced-tea, hot-chocolate
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: surfing, lacrosse, tennis
The people have 3 different jobs:  architect, designer, security-guard
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, tiparillo, baccarat
1. the alhambra-smoker is on the right of the security-guard##1
2. the architect is on the left of the baccarat-smoker##1
3. the person drinking tea is between the person who's sport is lacrosse and the person who's sport is tennis##2
4. the alhambra-smoker is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
5. the security-guard is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |
| Beverage         | iced-tea | tea   | hot-chocolate   |
| Sport   | lacrosse     | surfing | tennis |
| Job   | security-guard  | architect    | designer      |
| Cigar     | tiparillo     | alhambra      | baccarat |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: water, milk, fanta
There are 3 different favourite colors: yellow, apricot, white
3 different games are played: poker, go, bridge
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: western, romance, epic
1. the person who likes white is on the left of the person watching romance movies##1
2. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person who likes white##1
3. the person drinking milk is the person playing bridge##1
4. the person drinking water is the person playing go##1
5. the person watching western movies is between the person who likes apricot and the person drinking fanta##2
6. the person drinking fanta is the person watching romance movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3      |
| Beverage          | milk  | water     | fanta     |
| Color   | apricot     | white     | yellow      |
| Game   | bridge  | go | poker |
| Movie-Genre           | epic | western     | romance       |

