.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-3::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: surfing, biathlon, ice-hockey
There are 3 different nationalities: chinese, australian, pakistani
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: begonia, balloon-flower, marigold
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, pall-mall, bolivar
1. the chinese is on the left of the person who growsmarigold##1
2. the havana-smoker is between the pakistani and the person who growsmarigold##2
3. the person who's sport is surfing is on the far left##1
4. the pall-mall-smoker is the person who's sport is biathlon##1
5. the havana-smoker is the person who growsballoon-flower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |
| Sport          | surfing  | ice-hockey     | biathlon     |
| Nationality           | pakistani | chinese  | australian   |
| Flower   | begonia  | balloon-flower    | marigold |
| Cigar           | bolivar     | havana | pall-mall |

