.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-4::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: adventure, sports, crime
City: hamburg, rome, hannover
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: sunflower, tulip, aconite
There are 3 different favourite beverages: milk, cola, coffee
1. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person who growstulip##1
2. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person traveling to hannover##1
3. the person watching crime movies is between the person traveling to rome and the person who growssunflower##2
4. the person watching sports movies is the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |     2      |     3      |
| Movie-Genre    | adventure       | crime  | sports   |
| City     | rome    | hannover  | hamburg |
| Flower     | tulip   | aconite | sunflower        |
| Beverage   | coffee | milk     | cola      |

