There are 3 different nationalities: chinese, egyptian, polish
The people use 3 different means of transport: helicopter, snowmobile, roller
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, fanta, almond-milk
1. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
2. the person drinking coffee is between the person driving the roller and the polish##2
3. the chinese is the person drinking fanta##1
4. the prince-smoker is on the right of the bongani-smoker##1
5. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the bluemaster-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| Cigar          | bongani    | prince     | bluemaster      |
| Nationality         | chinese | egyptian | polish |
| Transport   | roller  | snowmobile       | helicopter       |
| Beverage           | fanta     | coffee       | almond-milk     |

