2. the dannemann-smoker is the lawyer##1
3. the person who growsdaffodil is between the swisher-smoker and the person playing mah-jongg##2
4. the person who growspoppy is on the far right##1
5. the chaman-smoker is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |
| Cigar          | swisher | chaman | dannemann    |
| Job         | police-officer | engineer      | lawyer |
| Flower   | aconite   | daffodil     | poppy        |
| Game           | scrabble      | monopoly       | mah-jongg      |

