.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-7::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: azure, aquamarine, purple
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: july, november, may
3 different games are played: domino, poker, whist
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: rose, tulip, daffodil
1. the person who growstulip is on the right of the person playing domino##1
2. the person who's birthday is in november is between the person who likes purple and the person who growsrose##2
3. the person playing poker is on the right of the person who likes aquamarine##1
4. the person who growsrose is on the far right##1
5. the person who's birthday is in november is between the person who's birthday is in may and the person playing domino##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |     3     |
| Color          | purple      | aquamarine   | azure |
| Birthday         | july | november | may |
| Game   | domino      | whist | poker   |
| Flower     | daffodil         | tulip  | rose       |

