3 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, dannemann, oliveros
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: december, june, january
1. the person traveling to venice is on the left of the dannemann-smoker##1
2. the person traveling to rome is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
3. the person who's birthday is in june is in the middle##1
4. the person who's birthday is in june is between the mechanic and the musician##2
5. the oliveros-smoker is on the far left##1
6. the musician is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |      3      |
