.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-12::.
3 different games are played: chess, monopoly, billiard
House: cape-cod, farmhouse, cottage
The people have 3 different hobbies: card-games, collecting, dancing
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, swisher, game
1. the person playing monopoly is the cottage house##1
2. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
3. the old-henry-smoker is on the left of the game-smoker##1
4. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
5. the person playing monopoly is between the farmhouse house and the person who's hobby is collecting##2
6. the person who's hobby is card-games is the game-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |       3        |
| Game      | chess | monopoly      | billiard            |
| House           | cape-cod | cottage | farmhouse |
| Hobby   | collecting     | dancing        | card-games         |
| Cigar   | swisher  | old-henry    | game        |

