.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-14::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, bus, motorbike
The people have 3 different hobbies: baking, dancing, chess
There are 3 different nationalities: japanese, nigerian, polish
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: lacrosse, skiing, soccer
1. the person driving the motorbike is between the person who's sport is skiing and the person who's hobby is chess##2
2. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the japanese##1
3. the polish is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
4. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
5. the person who's hobby is baking is the person who's sport is skiing##1
6. the japanese is on the right of the polish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2        |       3       |
| Transport      | bus    | motorbike          | car |
| Hobby          | chess | dancing           | baking        |
| Nationality           | nigerian | polish | japanese         |
| Sport   | lacrosse    | soccer    | skiing      |

