3. the gothic-revival house is on the far left##1
4. the chef is the person who likes purple##1
5. the accountant is on the left of the modern house##1
6. the modern house is on the left of the person who likes purple##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2     |      3       |
| House       | gothic-revival | modern | colonial |
