.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-17::.
There 3 different types of food: peach, carrot, onion
3 different games are played: snooker, go, monopoly
There are 3 different favourite beverages: juice, fanta, milk
There are 3 different favourite colors: white, purple, apricot
1. the person playing go is between the person who likes apricot and the person playing snooker##2
2. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person who likes apricot##1
3. the person eating carrot is the person drinking juice##1
4. the person drinking milk is the person eating peach##1
5. the person who likes white is the person drinking fanta##1
6. the person playing snooker is on the right of the person who likes purple##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |
| Food   | carrot | peach  | onion     |
| Game   | monopoly    | go | snooker |
| Beverage           | juice        | milk   | fanta  |
| Color     | apricot      | purple   | white |

