The people use 3 different means of transport: roller, airplane, bike
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: july, october, march
3 different games are played: mah-jongg, bridge, snooker
1. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
2. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person traveling to hannover##1
3. the person driving the bike is the person playing mah-jongg##1
4. the person traveling to berlin is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
5. the person driving the roller is on the far right##1
6. the person traveling to prague is between the person traveling to hannover and the person who's birthday is in october##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |    3     |
| City           | berlin   | prague   | hannover |
| Transport   | bike | airplane   | roller     |
| Birthday   | october     | july      | march    |
| Game           | mah-jongg | bridge | snooker    |

