3. the person eating apple is between the blend-smoker and the person driving the quad-bike##2
4. the person eating pineapple is the person traveling to marseilles##1
5. the person traveling to paris is between the fonseca-smoker and the person eating pineapple##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |      2      |      3      |
| Cigar      | blend | swisher     | fonseca        |
| Transport         | train   | bike | quad-bike |
| Food   | pineapple        | apple       | onion      |
| City           | marseilles           | paris    | london       |

