.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-20::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: magic-tricks, filmmaking, video-games
3 different games are played: monopoly, mah-jongg, chess
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: zinnia, amaryllis, marigold
The people have 3 different jobs:  social-worker, accountant, writer
1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person who growsamaryllis##1
2. the person playing mah-jongg is the social-worker##1
3. the person who growsamaryllis is the social-worker##1
4. the person who growszinnia is the person who's hobby is video-games##1
5. the person playing chess is between the writer and the person who growsamaryllis##2
6. the person who growsmarigold is the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |
| Hobby        | filmmaking      | magic-tricks | video-games |
| Game         | mah-jongg     | chess    | monopoly        |
| Flower       | amaryllis | marigold   | zinnia   |
| Job   | social-worker          | accountant     | writer       |

 